Integrating a Restitution Claim Form into your community hub (Discord or Website) is the bridge between user loss and protocol recovery. This form acts as a legal and technical submission to your Frostnerjo (FNR) recovery engine, ensuring that only verified identity owners can claim the Frostcoin (FTC) restoration rewards.
1. The Frost Protocol: Restitution Claim Form
This form should be pinned in a private #claims-portal channel on your Discord. It follows the DOGE (Do Only Good Everyday) principle by helping users who have suffered legacy Bitcoin losses.
